{
  "stem": "24409.10",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Authority.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, very well.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody tried to be Uncle Sam to me, to tell me how happy-- everybody gave me America.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were very nice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was very much upset about the lack of knowledge, of understanding-- lack of understanding on the part of most American Jews.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had arrived shortly before Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I went to the synagogue and through something I'm walking mid-Manhattan, and [INAUDIBLE] in a few minutes it was between [INAUDIBLE] or between the Torah readings, so there was not much going on.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were standing around me, a Jew from Europe, and they asked questions.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the questions were so-- showing so much of lack of understanding.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The most typical one was by one man who said, tell me, the Jews are supposed to be intelligent people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why do they not make shalom with Hitler?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why do they not make peace with Hitler?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was such a complete not knowledge of what was going on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But most were concerned about the state of the Jews in, in Europe, they were.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "How did you make your living?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I started earning money amazingly fast.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went first to the HIAS, as everybody did, and asked what they suggested I should do.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they said, so you don't have big eyes and big expectations, we'll help you.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We suggest that you try to get into the work with this [INAUDIBLE] in New Jersey.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There's always demand for people to work in this field.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I said, thank you very much.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I didn't need anything from them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I had about $80, which was good enough.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I always lived from one day to the other, but I was used to live on big style, you know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I had to in order to impress.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
